{"word":"G4959 - συστενάζω - systenázō - soos-ten-ad'-zo - Groan together","slug":"G4959","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συστενάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>systenázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soos-ten-ad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Groan together"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03BD;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - sustenazo&#x0304;</b> - <i>soos-ten-ad'-zo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G4727\">G4727</a>; to <i>moan jointly</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>experience a common calamity:</i> - groan together."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4726\">G4726</a>, <a href=\"#/G4727\">G4727</a>"}]}